longBusinessSummary: Lea Bank AB provides various banking products and services in Norway, Finland, Sweden, Germany, Spain, Austria, and France. It provides savings and deposit accounts; consumer loans, including car, boat, and motorcycle loans, as well as renovation, holiday, and Wedding loans; refinancing; payment insurance products; credit cards loan; and other financial services. Lea Bank AB was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
